dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"口口<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/123754_3c660295fe2d3828dbb89c482e6021cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F123754_3c660295fe2d3828dbb89c482e6021cd.jpg&h=242996c7&s={SIZE}\" />唔記得貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a001dba2737933852f8d64191050d88e3a0733","tid":359163,"uid":84683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"812ce7586da7ec38708fdc954ee9fda6309c175b","tid":359163,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:59:31.000Z","msg":"點先可以寫靚d"},{"pid":"f7bfd5d065dbcc528582239379b26b221123686c","tid":359163,"uid":56440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先可以寫靚d</blockquote><br />\n有冇用字帖？從楷書開始練"},{"pid":"fbf9f05550b9f235c84f2fb8e4f4656664da8f0b","tid":359163,"uid":56440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先可以寫靚d</blockquote><br />\n忙字個結構唔平均，練田字格有幫助<br />\n叫字個一棟唔直<br />\n就字冇咗尤個一勾<br />\n<br />\n注意多啲細位嚟執同練多啲"},{"pid":"8b24f86bffb01080c50adcc147455dc50bdc05c4","tid":359163,"uid":56440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/184234_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F184234_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=14449bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我都練緊字，控制唔好個行距同字體比例"},{"pid":"9a2fe9f5e22f272d42a170d5e8a9e05d5c3f6261","tid":359163,"uid":137988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"去書局買啲字帖返嚟抄啦，每日抄少少，手字好快靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7099b033205e3ba0645fcec4cd10044925ccff9","tid":359163,"uid":84683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"練字唔洗急<br />\n一筆一筆咁寫<br />\n<br />\n建議初學用格仔紙寫<br />\n練每隻字嘅比例大細"},{"pid":"afb74a930e3d95e9b1e163850ff2158bf3df0fb5","tid":359163,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/094023_7115771aa9ab28776bdbdbfec717efc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F094023_7115771aa9ab28776bdbdbfec717efc6.jpg&h=164f5050&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dca08f7b3c696323c285e375b7f5736c59bea5a","tid":359163,"uid":103340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"一開始練<br />\n首先，矯正左個姿勢先<br />\n如果姿勢無太大問題<br />\n就搵支啱自己嘅筆<br />\n我一開始寫就用鉛筆，<br />\n紙其實買好啲嘅<br />\n會易拎到手感<br />\n個人推中南嘅格仔紙<br />\n覺得貴用文格紙都好過你果款"},{"pid":"abe87e711f2b6937efc6f54712cf25a28409e1fc","tid":359163,"uid":103340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/184234_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F184234_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=14449bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我都練緊字，控制唔好個行距同字體比例</blockquote><br />\n其實練字距同行距真係難<br />\n就算墊左格仔係下面<br />\n都會寫唔正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人都係話練多啲"},{"pid":"6dbf49a6ac475fca295675f987670170be437377","tid":359163,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"點解橫紙要直寫"},{"pid":"2787d85fc47a891946123a4175b2e8d83a321bcc","tid":359163,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/120